plyTime":"2020-06-17T20:32:35.000Z","msg":"先乘除後加減"},{"pid":"6323cc23fe2aae57dbad2ab65678537ee97c250c","tid":2068594,"uid":195166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:33:18.000Z","msg":"識人好過識字"},{"pid":"90fe21b721bcc9918fb5b01f96b2dcf6919a5a55","tid":2068594,"uid":37246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:34:46.000Z","msg":"留名睇最多正評"},{"pid":"2d6015b8242462639153277bab6d3cf2944f5195","tid":2068594,"uid":307619,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:42:02.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"de78117ce04db88bd7b51304bba01735fa977143","tid":2068594,"uid":129335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:44:57.000Z","msg":"對任何人都要有警覺性"},{"pid":"02104b3e9